manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Choose the GX-850 PRO Power Supply and experience the ultimate in power and performance Designed to provide reliable power and consistent performance, the GX-850 PRO Power Supply is an essential component for any high-performance computer. With 80 PLUS GOLD certification, the GX-850 PRO Power Supply boasts superior energy efficiency, reducing heat generation and energy consumption. The ATX3.0 compliant design ensures seamless compatibility with most motherboards, while the Native PCIe 5.0 technology supports the latest graphics cards, providing you with the highest level of gaming graphics. The GX-850 PRO Power Supply packs an impressive 850W of power, ensuring your computer system is powered up and ready for anything you throw at it. Whether you're gaming or working on intensive tasks, the GX-850 PRO Power Supply delivers the power and stability you need to achieve peak performance. Built with high-quality materials and advanced technology, the GX-850 PRO Power Supply is designed to provide reliable and consistent power. Its built-in protection safeguards your computer against power surges and overloading, ensuring that your computer remains in peak condition.

NATIVE PCIE 5.0 The GX850 PRO power supply integrates a 12VHPWR 16-pin graphics card power connector, and comes with a high-quality original 16-pin cable. Which can provide complete power supply for RTX4090Ti and PCIE 5.0 graphics cards, and can support 600W continuous power output. COMPREHENSIVE CIRCUITPROTECTION Provide safety protection measures, with multiple protection technologies such as overload, overvoltage, undervoltage, overcurrent, short circuit, and interference, to protect the stability of the computer host and accessories,and avoid damage and interference. LARGE SIZE FAN FOR FAST HEAT DISSIPATION 135mm fan for high heat original cooling needs. Let you play games on is computer without crashing and blue screen.

HIGH QUALITY JAPANESEMAIN CAPACITOR GX850 PRO Main Capacitor Used the Japanese Capacitor 'Nichicon', High Temperature up to 105°C. FULL MODULAR DESIGNFLAT WIRE Full module design, sufficient power supply interface, hosting dual CPUs, or flagship graphics card three 8pin interfaces, flat wires make the wiring neat and beautiful. 135MM CUSTOMIZED F.D.B FAN The fan starts when the power consumption is higher than 20%, and stops when it is lower. The FDB fluid dynamic bearing fan avoids metal friction between traditional ball bearings and effectively reduces fan noise.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I've had it in my gaming pc running a i9 12900k and a gtx 4070 ti for over a month with no issues. Doesn't hurt that it, and the cables it comes with, match my white case.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Started to have issues, then died after 7 months
reviews.reviewText: I started having issues with this PSU about a month ago. My PC would cycle on a off randomly. Initially I thought I may have exceeded the wattage since I added an SSD and HDD so I upgraded to a larger Corsair unit. I put this into my partner's build and unfortunately ran into the same issues. We replaced cables, swapped the CMOS, and reseated everything. The PSU no longer turns on at all.The support is non-existent. I emailed a havn't heard anything back. Also, their website/method of contact seems very sketchy and had to work around some things even to send an email to their general info address. No access to an actual support line. Very very disappointed and would not suggest this product. Ya get what you pay for...

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Full mod, works great. Ventilation is good, doesn't run loud, all cables were present and it even came with some supplies for cable routing. Looks good both in and out of build. What more could you want from a PSU (aside from rgb, but they make a version for that too)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent price/performance for 1000 watt power supply
reviews.reviewText: Powering my 78003xd/xt7900xtx build. No news is good news with power supplies. This ps is handling my system with plenty of room for expansion. One of the better 1000 watt power supplies at its price range. Very good deal.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Worked great for my AMD AM5 build
reviews.reviewText: I got this to match my new build which was in a Thermaltake Tower 500 chassis (Snow white). So, I wanted a power supply that matched it. I'll say this... it matched GREAT! but is invisible to the user since the power supply is hidden, so I guess it didn't need to be white. However, the power cables that came with it are all white, so it matched up the build really well. There's plenty of plugs for everything and then some With 1250W, there's plenty of overhead in case I want to add anything else to the PC. Let's hope this power supply lasts a lifetime.

Fonte top, custo beneficio, em fevereiro vai fazer 1 ano que estou com ela, já liguei 2 RX 580 para rodar ao mesmo tempo, uma direcionada para jogos e a outra para o Encode no OBS STUDIO... e foi tranquilo, atualmente estou com essa RTX 4060.

reviews.reviewTitle: Ótima qualidade e excelente custo beneficio
reviews.reviewText: É uma fonte que supriu de forma absoluta meu setup não dando absolutamente nenhum problema em cerca de 1 ano de uso. Meu setup atualmente tem um Processador Ryzen 5 5600 G, uma RTX 3060 12GB, dois pentes de 8GB de RAM 3200Hz uma placa mãe A320 da Asus, um M2 de 512GB e um HD de 1TB.
Veio um pouco amassado a caixa mas a fonte veio perfeitamente, fonte muito bonita e com ótima qualidade

reviews.reviewTitle: tá caro mas tá top. (o que não está caro hoje em dia?)
reviews.reviewText: Essas fontes estão bem caras, comprei a minha por 420 em 2022. Vi que chega até 500 reais, mas a qualidade dela é bem boa, ótima fonte mesmo.

Quanto a entrega: Chegou antes do previsto.Quando ao produto: Instalei no mesmo dia, achei a caixa pequena em vista da imagem, mas chegou bem embalada e lacrada, não veio amassada e ainda tinha um selo de que o produto era frágil.Achei muito linda, todos os cabos pretos, porém, achei eles muito maleáveis, inclusive o da tomada.Por enquanto está entregando o que vem descrito, e sem contar que ela é super silenciosa, então, entrega o que promete.Tenho hoje 2 monitores, 6 fans, uma placa de vídeo 4060 e 2 SSDs e 2 pentes de 8gb e um water cooler, fora os periféricos. Acredito que não terei problemas.
